                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for decomposing hydrogen iodide by utilizing hot flue gas of boiler",
                    "一种利用锅炉热烟气实现碘化氢分解的系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a system and a method for realizing hydrogen iodide decomposition by utilizing boiler hot flue gas. The system comprises a mixed liquid container, a mixed liquid pump, a pump outlet regulating valve, a boiler high-temperature flue gas area and a temperature control valve, an outlet of the mixed liquid container is connected to an inlet of the mixed liquid pump, an outlet of the mixed liquid pump is connected to an inlet of the pump outlet adjusting valve, an outlet of the pump outlet adjusting valve is connected to an inlet of the boiler high-temperature flue gas area, and an outlet of the boiler high-temperature flue gas area is connected to an inlet of the temperature control valve. Heat is obtained from the flue gas of the power station boiler, only the hydrogen iodide heating device needs to be placed in the high-temperature area of the boiler hearth, the two sides of the hydrogen iodide heating device are low in pressure, the safety of the hydrogen iodide heating device is greatly improved, in addition, heat is directly obtained from the flue gas, and the hydrogen iodide heating device is more economical compared with steam and electric energy."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种利用锅炉热烟气实现碘化氢分解的系统和方法，该系统包括混合液容器、混合液泵、泵出口调节阀、锅炉高温烟气区和温度控制阀；混合液容器的出口接至混合液泵的入口，混合液泵的出口接在泵出口调节阀的入口，泵出口调节阀的出口接在锅炉高温烟气区的入口，锅炉高温烟气区的出口接在温度控制阀的入口。本发明从电站锅炉烟气中获得热量，只需将碘化氢加热装置放置于锅炉炉膛高温区，碘化氢加热装置的两侧均为低压，大大提高其安全性，另外从烟气获得热量是直接获得热量，相较于蒸汽及电能来说更经济。"
                }
            ]
